{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glsl-token-depth\">glsl-token-depth</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"></a></p>\n<p>Determine the scope depth of an array of GLSL tokens.</p>\n<p>Useful for inferring the scope of variables in a GLSL shader without having\nto fully parse the source.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/glsl-token-depth/\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"depth-tokens-\"><code>depth(tokens)</code></h3>\n<p>Where <code>tokens</code> is an array of tokens returned from\n<a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glsl-tokenizer\"><code>glsl-tokenizer</code></a>. Each token will\nbe modified in-place, and given a <code>depth</code> property.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;tokenize&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;glsl-tokenizer/string&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;depth&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;glsl-token-depth&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;fs&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;fs&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;src&#xA0;=&#xA0;fs.readFileSync(&apos;shader.frag&apos;,&#xA0;&apos;utf8&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;tokens&#xA0;=&#xA0;tokenize(src)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>depth(tokens)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>tokens[0].depth&#xA0;//&#xA0;0</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>tokens[1].depth&#xA0;//&#xA0;0</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>tokens[2].depth&#xA0;//&#xA0;0</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>tokens[3].depth&#xA0;//&#xA0;0</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>tokens[4].depth&#xA0;//&#xA0;1</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>//&#xA0;...</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"see-also\">See Also</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glsl-tokenizer\">stackgl/glsl-tokenizer</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT. See <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glsl-token-depth/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">LICENSE.md</a> for details.</p>\n"}